Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳是我们太阳系的超级大国\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Sun is the superpower of our Solar System,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.97,0:00:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一座高热核反应堆 巨大的爆炸喷发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a thermonuclear blast furnace, erupting with massive explosions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它能将相当于珠穆朗玛峰那样质量的聚合物\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It can be the same amount of mass as mount Everest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从太阳抛出进入太空\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}coming out from the Sun and flying out into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.11,0:00:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们安全地在9300万英哩外看着太阳的狂怒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At 93 million miles away it would seem that we are safe from the Sun's wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我们？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是在当今关心的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It matters, especially in modern times,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳在干什么？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what the Sun is doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳旋转的中心\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}From the center of the Sun, as it rotates around,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如"死亡之区"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is the "kill zone".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些专家预测了现代太阳活动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With some experts predicting the most violent outbreak of solar activity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最剧烈的爆发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in modern history.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比任何时候都来的重要 去了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it never been more important to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the secrets of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0001,,{\fn华文楷体\fs16\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0}--==本影片由 {\1c&HFF8000&\b1}CMCT 团队{\fn华文楷体\1c&H3CF1F3&\b0} 荣誉出品==--\N更多精彩影视 请访问 {\fnCronos Pro Subhead\1c&HFF00FF&\b1}http://www.hdcmct.com{\r}
