Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时离开太阳表面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}leaving the surface of the Sun all at once.
