Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一个大的耀斑一次充分发出足够的能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}If a large flare shoots enough high energy particles at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇异的事情开始产生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}strange things start to happen.
