Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达到每小时25万英哩的速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}250 thousand miles per hour.
