Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在太阳上地震不是唯一的天灾\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Earthquakes aren't the only natural disasters with equivalents on the Sun.
