Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时在太空里无害地航行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Sometimes it sails out harmlessly into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他时候可能会接近我们的家园\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Other times it may head closer to home.
