Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国国家海洋与大气管理局的总部\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration,
